items.title: Gigabyte GV-R67XTGAMING OC-12GD AMD, 12 GB, Radeon RX 6700 XT, GDDR6
items.description: The AMD Radeon RX 6700 XT graphics card, powered by AMD RDNA 2 architecture, is a new generation of performance-class graphics card that plays the latest AAA titles with ultra smooth framerate at FHD and 1440 resolution. An array of advanced technologies is built in to optimize your gaming experience by sharpening images, reducing input lag, and minimizing frame tear.
